snippet.title: Arc Raiders - Blue Gate (NEW Map) Unleashing the Hullcracker Weapon | Exclusive First Look
snippet.description:
*Our NEW 'Topside' Merch Is Now Available*
Sweatshirt - https://www.tiktok.com/t/ZPHvE6LQtLoJY-p4SDW/

Today, Codiak and Livid break down a round within the brand new map, Blue Gate, not previously seen anywhere in Arc Raiders until today. We not only showcase the brand new Hullcracker epic weapon, but also share some of our favorite tips for navigating this new map. Taking out elite enemies like Basions, Bombardiers, and Rocketeers while exploring brand new POIs and getting into PvP fights - it's all here in this video.
